{"tid":1053480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘遭變態男性侵玩殘　3歲女童染2種性病","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T10:53:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"57cbcdee52516b84d7f285e20ba83b65d30c228c","tid":1053480,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"美國德州一名26歲男子博金斯(Drevon Alexander Perkins)毫無人性，對一名3歲女童性侵，更導致女童罹患2種性病。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，博金斯在今年1月潛伏在女童住家附近，待女童的母親外出上班後，博金斯潛入屋裡性侵女童。之後母親回家，發現女兒的尿布被噴了大量體液，且不像是女童的尿液，立刻將女童送醫，更被驗出染上披衣菌(chlamydia)與淋病(gonorrhea)。警方之後循線逮捕博金斯，他承認犯行，並被驗出身上同樣罹患披衣菌與淋病，相信是由他傳染給女童。<br />\n博金斯目前已被控訴最嚴重的性侵兒童罪，至少面臨25年以上徒刑，他目前被以10萬美元(約新台幣300萬元)交保。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190309/640_222cda04b3359440c60e00b97c838745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190309%2F640_222cda04b3359440c60e00b97c838745.jpg&h=4417f3d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190309/1530078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190309%2F1530078%2F&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=83ae2b66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190309%2F1530078%2F&h=adcb36cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190309/1530078/</a>"},{"pid":"dec5ed9b71aae39fbb41b9873f68717dbda75a59","tid":1053480,"uid":233209,"like":6,"dislike":60,"score":-54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3df4ec7e25fcb37818524339f88b1129a819780","tid":1053480,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"